<h1>Download</h1>
<h4>Official releases at SourceForge</h4>

<p>
Official releases can be downloaded from SourceForge as
<a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/gtk-gnutella/files/" target="_blank">source tarballs</a>.
Cryptographic signatures for the tarballs are also available. 
</p>

<h4>Software distributions</h4>

<p>
gtk-gnutella is available from several software distributions.
</p>

<h5>Linux</h5>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://rpmfind.net/linux/rpm2html/search.php?query=gtk-gnutella" target="_blank">Fedora</a></li>
<li><a href="http://packages.gentoo.org/package/net-p2p/gtk-gnutella" target="_blank">Gentoo</a></li>
<li><a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/search?keywords=gtk-gnutella" target="_blank">Ubuntu</a> <strong>[Terribly outdated version!]</strong> download <a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/gtk-gnutella/files/gtk-gnutella/" target="_blank">the latest .deb package from SourceForge</a></li>
<li>Debian: we submitted the request to add back the .deb package into the Debian repository; in the meanwhile download <a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/gtk-gnutella/files/gtk-gnutella/" target="_blank">the latest package from SourceForge</a></li>
</ul>

<h5>BSD</h5>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.freshports.org/net-p2p/gtk-gnutella/" target="_blank">FreshPorts - FreeBSD packages</a></li>
<li><a href="http://pkgsrc.se/net/gtk-gnutella" target="_blank">pkgsrc - The NetBSD package collection</a></li>
</ul>

<h5>Windows</h5>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/gtk-gnutella/files/gtk-gnutella/" target="_blank">The latest .exe installation
	package is available from SourceForge</a></li>
</ul>

<h5>Mac OS X</h5>
<ul>
<li>Sorry but .dmg packages for Mac OS X are not currently available!</li>
<li><a href="http://pdb.finkproject.org/pdb/package.php/gtk-gnutella" target="_blank">Fink</a> <strong>[Terribly outdated version!]</strong></li>
</ul>

<p>
These are the most convenient options for installing gtk-gnutella but the provided version of gtk-gnutella may be outdated.
</p>

<p>
Please, report any bugs and problems with gtk-gnutella at our
<a href="?lang=en&page=mailing">mailing lists</a> or <a href="?lang=en&page=bugreport_howto">bug tracker</a>!
</p>

